details.biography:
Grace Gummer is an American actress who received a Theatre World Award for her Broadway debut in the 2011 revival of Arcadia. Her television work includes recurring roles on the HBO series The Newsroom (2013–14), and the FX series American Horror Story: Freak Show (2014–15), as well as regular roles on the CBS series Extant (2014–15) and USA series Mr. Robot (2016–present).

Her mother is award-winning actress Meryl Streep and her sister Mamie is also an actress.
details.name: Grace Gummer
details.place_of_birth: New York City, New York, USA
